Text: Re Counterparty Approval List Cc I dont think this is meant for me I did not receive an email from Tana John From Samantha NRON on CDT To John CT Molly CT cc Tana CT Subject Counterparty Approval List Per Tana Joness email dated June I should have received a copy of the counterparty approval list to distribute in her absence Please advise at your earliest convenience if a list was distributed on today I will be in training tomorrow However during my lunch hour I will check my email for a response from you Thanks for your attention to this matter Samantha M Boyd X
